{
  "stem": "95.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And she would feed them raw meat and all these things that we never had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "She-- and experiments.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "She was doing experiments.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Not experiments-- she would-- she would line up people with tattoos on their chest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And if she liked the tattoo on their chest, she would say, you, out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And then she would kill them and skin the tat-- the skin and make lamp shades out of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I mean, that's what she was doing, this woman who was the wife of the commandant of Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I think she got caught after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They probably hanged her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Like Tom Mix got-- I've heard, after the war, that Tom Mix did get-- did get catched.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "They caught him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They caught Mix.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I've been in this country for so long, I still don't know how to speak English.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Anyway, they caught him, and he got hanged for what he did, which was fine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Anyway, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they sent us into the little camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Now again, I was saved in Buchenwald by four non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "The head of the delousing department was a-- was a German communist who was there since 1937.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Why he picked me out of the 1,200 people who arrived there and saved my life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "While we were waiting to be disinfected and shaved, he gave me a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "Then he knew what barracks we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "We were put into the theater-- 1,200 people in one big theater.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "We were standing in line to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "We all had dysentery, and it was-- it was just terrible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And-- and there he is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "He comes in the barrack and talks to me and give me another piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
